  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/416007742" />
    <a title="Lucinda Hill" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11840609-lucinda-hill"><img alt="Lucinda Hill" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1344905384p2/11840609.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/416007742?book_show_action=true">Sep 16, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lucinda Hill" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lucinda Hill" href="/user/show/11840609-lucinda-hill">Lucinda Hill</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780983348061" href="/book/show/13825969-thoughts-for-the-day">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer416007742" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12274433119656324768">In this book are many scripture based thoughts . I found comfort in being reminded of how much God loves me. I found inspiration to always try to improve on myself. And I found encouragement in the thoughts of our future in Heaven. Great book to pick up and read on a daily basis.<br/>Lucinda<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


